        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "三、化学方程式的书写",
        "bbox": [
          0.14913341394598953,
          0.08664671512042184,
          0.3305118903667876,
          0.10260795211628901
        ],
        "order": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_1",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1、知识讲解",
        "bbox": [
          0.14993954050785974,
          0.10602821718683197,
          0.25070536074163646,
          0.1208493658258515
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_2",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1.化学方程式的书写原则遵循两个原则： 一是必须以客观事实为基础，绝不能凭空设想、主观臆造事实上不存在的物质和化学反 应。 二是遵循质量守恒定律，即方程式两边各种原子的种类和数目必须相等。",
        "bbox": [
          0.17492946392583636,
          0.1305401168590566,
          0.8206368399838775,
          0.20806612512469716
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2.化学计量数：",
        "bbox": [
          0.17573559048770657,
          0.2126264785520878,
          0.28053204353083433,
          0.2274476271911073
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "化学计量数指配平化学方程式后，化学式前面的数字。在化学方程式中，各化学式前的 化学计量数之比应是最简整数比，计数量为1时，一般不写出。",
        "bbox": [
          0.17654171704957677,
          0.23257802479692177,
          0.8182184602982668,
          0.26906085221604675
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "3.化学方程式中“↑”和“↓”的应用：",
        "bbox": [
          0.17654171704957677,
          0.2736212056434374,
          0.4207980652962515,
          0.2890123984608807
        ],
        "order": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_6",
        "observed_type": "list",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（1）“↑”或“↓”是生成物状态符号，无论反应物是气体还是固体，都不能标“个”或“↓”; （2）若反应在溶液中进行且生成物中有沉淀，则使用“↓”；若不在溶液中进行，无论生 成物中是否有固体或难溶物，都不使用“↓”； （3）常温下，若反应物中体，成物中有体.则标出“↑”。",
        "bbox": [
          0.17815397017331722,
          0.29357275188827137,
          0.8206368399838775,
          0.3710987601539119
        ],
        "order": 7
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_7",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "4.化学方程式的配平：",
        "bbox": [
          0.16364369205965337,
          0.3910503063987459,
          0.32889963724304716,
          0.4070115433946131
        ],
        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_8",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "根据质量守恒定律，反应前后原子的种类和数目不变，在反应物和生成物的化学式前配 上适当的化学计量数，使各种元素的原子个数在反应前后相等。",
        "bbox": [
          0.16444981862152358,
          0.4127119851788514,
          0.8335348649738009,
          0.44976485677640016
        ],
        "order": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0002",
    "kind": "text_cluster_panel",
    "page": "jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751",
    "primary_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_9",
    "source": "text_cluster",
    "member_count": 6,
    "elements": [
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_9",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "具体步骤：",
        "bbox": [
          0.16444981862152358,
          0.4548952543822146,
          0.24506247480854493,
          0.4708564913780818
        ],
        "order": 10
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_10",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（1）写：根据实验事实写出反应物和生成物的化学式。反应物在左，生成物在右，中 间用横线连接，如：H₂+O2——H₂O；",
        "bbox": [
          0.1652559451833938,
          0.47655693316232006,
          0.8295042321644498,
          0.5141798489382927
        ],
        "order": 11
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_11",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（2）配：根据反应前后原子的种类和数目不变的原则，在反应物和生成物的化学式前 配上适当的化学计量数，使各种元素的原子个数在反应前后相等，然后将横线变成等 号。配平后，化学式前的化学计量数之比应是最简整数比，如:2H₂+O2=2H2O；",
        "bbox": [
          0.1652559451833938,
          0.5187402023656833,
          0.8278919790407094,
          0.5780247969217615
        ],
        "order": 12
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_12",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（3）注：注明反应条件如点燃、加热（常用“△\"表示）、光照、通电等和生成物的状态（ 气体用“↑”。沉淀用“↓”。)。如：2H2+O2 点2H2O，2H2O通电2H2↑+O2↑。 配平常用方法：",
        "bbox": [
          0.1652559451833938,
          0.582585150349152,
          0.826279725916969,
          0.6452900099757731
        ],
        "order": 13
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "（1）最小公倍数法",
        "bbox": [
          0.16848045143087464,
          0.6498503634031637,
          0.3184199919387344,
          0.665811600399031
        ],
        "order": 14
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_1751_14",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "①找出化学程式左、右两边各出现次，且原子个数既不相等又相对较多的元素，求",
        "bbox": [
          0.1596130592503023,
          0.6715120421832692,
          0.8335348649738009,
          0.6874732791791364
        ],
        "order": 15
      }
    ]
  }
]